msgstr "État final après clôture du marché ou annulation manuelle de l'ordre"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
msgid "**rejected**"
msgstr "Often `rejected`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/3-risk-and-order-lifecycle.md
